    <h1>Plat&#xAD;form shoes and other fall trends</h1>
    <h2>Fall/Win&#xAD;ter run&#xAD;way trends aim to buoy spir&#xAD;its with bold bro&#xAD;cades, pow&#xAD;er&#xAD;ful sleeves and shoes made for stomp&#xAD;ing</h2>
